  "title": "English Specialist Curriculum Mentor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Review and refine the English curriculum (phonics, reading, writing, oral language)</p></li><li><p>Coach and mentor teachers through lesson observations and feedback</p></li><li><p>Model best practices in English lessons (demo classes)</p></li><li><p>Support lesson planning, assessment, and differentiation</p></li><li><p>Align curriculum with ECDA frameworks</p></li><li><p>Conduct workshops or training sessions for teachers</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Strong background in <strong>early childhood English / literacy</strong></p></li><li><p>Experience as a <strong>curriculum mentor</strong></p></li><li><p>Familiar with <strong>phonics-based approaches</strong> and early literacy development</p></li><li><p>ECDA-recognised qualifications preferred</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication and mentoring skills</p></li></ul>",
