    "description": "<p>Welcome to Superland – where little ones from around the world gather daily to explore, discover and expand their social circle. In Superland, children develop not just head knowledge but also heart knowledge. Every child is valued, respected and loved!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Superland has been making a difference to the lives of thousands of children since 2002. Our preschool offers a safe and nurturing environment for local and expatriate children aged 2 months to 6 years. Here, the Montessori teaching approach is combined with our thoughtfully-crafted bilingual curriculum and delivered in a fun and creative way to keep your child inspired to learn.</p>",
